OL,3,CPolice investigate funeral directors
OL,4,Cover 'care' of bodies
OL,6,FDet Ch Supt Simon Gawthorpe said:
OL,7,F"Whilst we are in the very early
OL,8,Fstages of our investigation, I
OL,9,Fcompletely understand this information
OL,10,Fwill be of concern to a number of
OL,11,Ffamilies and individuals who have lost
OL,12,Floved ones and have utilised the
OL,13,Fservices of this business."JThe
OL,14,Fcoroner, Hull City Council and East
OL,15,FRiding Council have been informed.
OL,17,FThe detective added: "I would
OL,18,Fencourage anyone to please call us, as
OL,19,Fwe are very mindful of the distress
OL,20,Fthis may cause."
