OL,6,FThe website added: "This means we
OL,7,Fadhere to their strict codes of
OL,8,Fpractice, and are passionate about
OL,9,Fensuring your family member or friend
OL,10,Fis looked after with the highest
OL,11,Flevels of professional care.
OL,13,F"We have a profound belief that a
OL,14,Fperson must be treated with reverence
OL,15,Fand dignity between their passing and
OL,16,Ftheir funeral, and we always go the
OL,17,Fextra mile to deliver on this
OL,18,Fprinciple."
