OL,6,FPolice called for people to "refrain
OL,7,Ffrom speculation" about what had
OL,8,Fhappened.
OL,10,FDet Ch Supt Gawthorpe said: "At the
OL,11,Fcore of this investigation will
OL,12,Fpotentially be heartbroken and
OL,13,Fdevastated families and loved ones and
OL,14,Fwe want to provide them with the
OL,15,Fconsideration and support they need
OL,16,Fand are fully entitled to."
OL,18,FAnyone with concerns can call 0800 051
OL,19,F4674.
